莫爾頓波傳播的[[速度|速度]]在每秒500-1500公里，並依據與電波[[II型爆發|II型爆發]]相關的著名[[Yutaka_Uchida|Yutaka Uchida]]理論，和色球產生交互作用發生冠狀[[磁流體動力學|磁流體動力學的]]快速模式弱衝激波。莫爾頓波主要是以Hα波段來觀測<ref name="Narukage, et al.">{{Cite journal|title=Moreton waves observed at Hida Observatory|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/product/identifier/S1743921304006143/type/journal_article|last=Narukage|first=Noriyuki|last2=Eto|first2=Shigeru|date=2004-06|journal=Proceedings of the International Astronomical Union|issue=IAUS223|doi=10.1017/S1743921304006143|volume=2004|pages=367–370|language=en|issn=1743-9213|last3=Kadota|first3=Miwako|last4=Kitai|first4=Reizaburo|last5=Kurokawa|first5=Hiroki|last6=Shibata|first6=Kazunari}}</ref>。

